@startuml component-dijagram
!theme plain
title Component dijagram — slojevita arhitektura (v1.0)

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
  BorderColor #555555
}

package "Presentation (Browser)" {
  [Inertia React SPA] as React
  [Tailwind 4] as Tailwind
  [Wayfinder gen] as Wayfinder
}

package "HTTP Layer" {
  [Controllers (Admin + Public)] as Controllers
  [Middleware (auth, role)] as Middleware
  [Form Requests] as FormRequests
}

package "Application Layer" {
  [TeamRegistrationService] as TRS
  [EDnevnikVerificationService] as EVS
  [ResultEntryService] as RES
  [AuditLogger] as AL
  [PrivateFileStorage] as PFS
  [MedicalCertificateStateMachine] as SM
}

package "Domain Layer" {
  [Eloquent Models (STI User, Student, Team...)] as Models
  [Policies] as Policies
  [Enums] as Enums
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
  [FakeOcrAdapter] as OcrAdapter
  [FakeEDnevnikAdapter] as EdnAdapter
  [Notifications (Mail+DB)] as Notif
  [Queue Jobs] as Jobs
}

cloud "Eksterni servisi" {
  [eDnevnik (mock dev / pravi prod)] as eDnevnik
  [Google Vision OCR (mock dev)] as Vision
  [AWS SES (log driver dev)] as SES
  database "Storage S3 (lokalno dev)" as S3
  database "DB SQLite dev / PostgreSQL prod" as DB
}

React --> Controllers : Inertia POST/GET
Wayfinder ..> React : type-safe rute
Controllers --> Middleware : kroz route group
Controllers --> FormRequests : validate()
Controllers --> TRS
Controllers --> EVS
Controllers --> RES
TRS --> Models
TRS --> AL
TRS --> Notif
TRS --> SM
EVS --> EdnAdapter
EVS --> Models
RES --> Models
RES --> AL
AL --> Models : AuditLogEntry
PFS --> S3
SM --> Models
Jobs --> OcrAdapter
Jobs --> EdnAdapter
Jobs --> Models
OcrAdapter ..> Vision : prod (iza feature flag)
EdnAdapter ..> eDnevnik : prod (iza feature flag)
Notif --> SES
Models --> DB
Policies ..> Models

@enduml
